folder: Rogers Avenue & Empire Boulevard, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Rogers Ave., and Empire Boulevard; a general view north west, about 1870.) This picture includes properties of the Chadwick, Boyton, Needham, Horgan and Miller families. At present (1936), Stoddard Place and Ludlow Place are
in this area.
About 1870.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
P3h E27

folder: Empire Boulevard & Rogers Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Empire Blvd., at the N.E. corner of Rogers Ave. A view of the Armstrong house, still standing in 1929.
1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
